You collect scrap metal all day to sell for a few coins. (+Wealth, -Health)
You learn to pick pockets to survive on the streets. (+Wealth, -EQ, +Luck if successful)
A shopkeeper catches you stealing bread but takes pity and gives you a job. (+Wealth, +EQ, +LoveReceiving)
You get sick from eating spoiled food found in the trash. (-Health, -Wealth)
You help a younger child find their parents, receiving a coin as thanks. (+EQ, +Wealth, +LoveReceiving)
You sleep in a cold doorway and wake up with a fever. (-Health, -Mental Health)
You discover a discarded book and teach yourself to read better. (+IQ, +Mental Health)
You are chased by a truancy officer and hide in a dumpster. (-Mental Health, +Luck)
You share your only blanket with a stray dog for warmth. (+EQ, -Health)
You find a lost wallet and return it, getting a small reward. (+Wealth, +EQ, +Luck)